<H3><A NAME="subj5.1">Re: The new Cray and Unix passwords...</A></H3>
<ADDRESS>
"Chris Ransom" 
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:chris@quests.com">chris@quests.com</A>&gt;
</ADDRESS>
<I>Thu, 25 Aug 94 09:45:13 PDT</I><PRE>
 
Mr. Wayner neglects to consider the "salt" values used to hash the passwords
which prevent this type of attack. All 1000 passwords would likely require
independent encryption with unique salt values.
 
Chris Ransom   <A HREF="mailto:chris@quests.com">chris@quests.com</A>

