<HR><H3><A NAME="subj10.3">Re: Bug in Microsoft Word (something similar in WriteNow?)</A></H3>
<ADDRESS>
"Anthony E. Siegman" 
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:siegman@Sierra.Stanford.EDU">siegman@Sierra.Stanford.EDU</A>&gt;
