</ADDRESS>
<I>Tue, 6 Sep 1994 14:17:01 +0100</I><PRE>

THE INSTITUTE OF MATHEMATICS AND ITS APPLICATIONS
Catherine Richards House, 16 Nelson Street, Southend-on-Sea, Essex, SS1 1EF.
