Newcastle NE1 7RU, UK  +44 91-222-8228  <A HREF="mailto:John.Dobson@newcastle.ac.uk">John.Dobson@newcastle.ac.uk</A>

Catherine Meadows, Naval Research Laboratory, Code 5543, Washington, DC 20375
+1 (202)-767-3490 (voice)  +1 (202)-404-7942 (fax)
<A HREF="mailto:meadows@itd.nrl.navy.mil">meadows@itd.nrl.navy.mil</A>

